OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be partly cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, heavy at first. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will see variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud and some showery rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FQuite cloudy in the west
OL,12,Fbut some bright or sunny spells in the
OL,13,Feast. A scattering of showers, these
OL,14,Fheavy in the north. Becoming drier
OL,15,Flater in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
