OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fon Thursday morning, and again later
OL,7,Fin the day. Dry with sunny spells on
OL,8,FFriday. Chance of some rain at first
OL,9,Fon Saturday, otherwise mainly dry.
OL,10,FWarm.
